data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED: Make every day a staycation! Nestled within a serene and vibrant community, this 5-bedroom, 4-bath home is ready to begin its next chapter under your ownership. Glistening hardwood floors and sunlight lead the way into a well-appointed kitchen that will delight where white cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances provide the perfect canvas for culinary creations. The expansive center island is large enough to accommodate three bar stools. But the real magic happens when you open the kitchen's sliding doors, inviting you to the screened-in outdoor patio, effortlessly connecting indoor and outdoor living. Back inside, the kitchen gives way to the indoor dining area and living room, allowing you to entertain in style regardless of the season. A more intimate family room can be found just upstairs with a large built-in entertainment center adorned with cabinets, shelving, and artistic spotlights. It's the ideal stage for showcasing your most cherished mementos and photos. Retreat to the private primary suite, where you'll find a luxurious ensuite bathroom complete with a separate shower and a deep soaking tub, offering an escape from the stresses of the day. Additional amenities include an HOA with access to a shimmering pool, tennis and basketball courts, and 24hr security. You'll have all you need to relax and unwind just steps from your front door. Your dream home is ready to welcome you with open arms. Don't miss the chance to make it yours.
